        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Your engagement ring photos deserve to be photographed in a way that feels natural, refined and effortless - just like the story of how you fell in love! Today’s couples are moving from overly polished photoshoots to clicking photographs that whisper a story without feeling posed. These are authentically yours! The most captivating <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement ring \">engagement ring </a>photos aren’t the ones that scream attention but the ones where the ring shines and reflects a beautiful moment. Whether you are preparing for your pre-wedding photoshoot or simply capturing personal memories, these engagement ring couple photos  elevate your ring as well as your love story. Each one of them are curated to look natural while capturing the beauty of your ring. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxFmqg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Car Mirror Reflection",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Car Mirror Reflection</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-car",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AynJ8F": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Car_Mirror_Reflection_f8b757bf-525b-4b96-a6e9-c9acbe1c132e.png",
            "text": "<p>There’s something timelessly romantic about memories created inside the car. Hands intertwined, music playing in the background, sunlight pouring in and smiles exchanged, while the world moves outside the window.<br/>To click the photo, park the car where there is soft, even sunlight. Harsh sunlight will create a glare on the mirror. Hold your hand, showing off your ring. Flip open the sun visor mirror and angle it to focus </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YCFMNY": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Car Mirror Paragraph",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>on your hands held together, metaphorically - for the rest of your lives as your journey goes forward. The reflection naturally puts the ring into the spotlight. This engagement ring hand photo feels personal, cinematic and beautiful. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "center"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lift & Laugh Moment the-lift ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lift & Laugh Moment the-lift </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-lift",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zpxzBh": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Lift_Laugh_Moment_the-lift_792d687a-9def-45f0-badd-86a3cb14aae3.png",
            "text": "<p>A lifted pose captures pure joy and motion. It is one of the very few engagement ring ceremony poses that reveals the ring beautifully in a candid way. In this picture, the groom lifts the bride from behind, making the bride lean forward towards the camera. Her face is lit up with a wide grin as she flaunts her ring. This hand pic with a ring blends emotion with elegance, allowing the ring to shine as part of a joyful story rather than the focal point.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "classic-cushion-cut-diamond-ring",
              "cushion-pear-cut-diamond-necklace"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Fiction And You - An Intimate And Editorial Pose",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Fiction And You - An Intimate And Editorial Pose</h2>",
            "custom_id": "fiction",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VWDmRU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fiction_And_You_-_An_Intimate_And_Editorial_Pose_fiction_54433740-aa24-448f-b022-e5789412a4cb.png",
            "text": "<p>She reads novels. She tells you the plot. It is a ritual, right? This pose captures a relaxed moment while letting the ring appear organically.</p><p>Create this picture by positioning yourselves in front of each other by the window. Use the window’s soft lighting pouring inside and click a photo of the bride reading/flipping the page, while the fiance looks at her admiringly. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "classic-solitaire-diamond-mangalsutra-bracelet",
              "amara-round-diamond-mangalsuta-bracelet",
              "6-05ct-delicate-round-diamond-tennis-bracelet",
              "apex-panther-diamond-mens-bracelet"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Fiction And You  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The groom can go an extra mile to add a layer of detail - by wearing her scrunchie on his wrist. </p><p>The result is refined, warm, homely and perfect for couples who appreciate understated luxury. Feel free to change the setting by clicking this picture in a garden or a bookstore. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Suitcase Shot    ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Suitcase Shot    </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-suitcase",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Suitcase_Shot_the-suitcase.png",
            "text": "<p>Travel inspired shots are exactly what youngsters are looking for as they suggest a beginning to a journey forward - one filled with adventure and partnership. To set up the positioning, bring two suitcases side by side. Both partners rest one hand naturally on the suitcase handles, rings facing outward but not forced.The frame now looks rich, modern and fun! Keep backgrounds simple with airport elements. This pose is perfect for editorial-style travel photography. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-51-ct-round-solitaire-diamond-ring",
              "0-40-ct-aegis-pear-solitaire-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dEkM3m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Rain-Kissed Moment   ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Rain-Kissed Moment </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-rain",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Rain-Kissed_Moment_the-rain_0b3fddbc-10ac-4fae-b130-cee0ff70dfaf.png",
            "text": "<p>Only a few settings can match the dramatic, cinematic view of the rain. For a picture that looks like it's straight out of a movie, just like your love story looks, use soft natural light. Overcast skies help set the mood of the picture. As the groom, cup her face gently with a smile on. The camera should be on the side of the hand where the ring shows. As the bride, place your hand with the ring on his chest or shoulder lovingly. Zoom in to take a close up.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8dndd7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Rain-Kissed Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> You can even edit your pictures with a black and white filter while the ring shines. This pose is both tender and dramatic - the perfect fusion to define a love story</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jMYfry": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The “Mr & Mrs” Coffee Cups",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The “Mr & Mrs” Coffee Cups</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-mr",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Mr_Mrs_Coffee_Cups_the-mr_ff767937-fbd6-49ea-88ae-1c7ee870dd12.png",
            "text": "<p>Does it feel like yesterday that you spent your early days getting to know each other over a cup of coffee? If yes, then this is for you. Wrap your hands over two takeaway cups as a couple, and let the rings show. To add a little detail and a context that warms the hearts of viewers, add labels of</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qXGmxM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The “Mr & Mrs” Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> Mr. and Mrs. and see how our hearts melt at the sight of this picture.This is one of the ring ceremony engagement couple poses that feels effortless and is symbolic. It is so naturally poetic, that it feels deeply personal and feels luxurious at the same time.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Matching Tattoos       ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Matching Tattoos  </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-matching",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Matching_Tattoos_the-matching.png",
            "text": "<p>If you are a couple with matching tattoos on the bucket list, this one is for you. This is less of a pose, and more of an idea for you to go the extra mile. This is for couples who admire layered meanings without having to caption an image saying - we are engaged! Ink your forever with tattoos saying ‘In this life’ on the groom’s hand and ‘in the next’ in the bride’s hand.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_KjzYqM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Matching Tattoos  Paragraph ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> Click a picture of these tattoos etched on your hands with the engagement ring showing in the frame. A clean, neutral background keeps the focus on the message. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hEAXhx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Quick Note on Choosing a Ring That Photographs Beautifully",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A Quick Note on Choosing a Ring That Photographs Beautifully</h2>",
            "custom_id": "a-quick",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTfgNx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Quick Note on Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Before you try on poses, remember this: the right ring naturally looks good. Just like some human faces are photogenic, so are rings! Some rings just reflect light better than the others. These are diamonds with brilliant cut grades and have prong settings that maximize the sparkle of the ring. </p><p>If you are still looking for rings or planning an upgrade, look for the features that make a ring look beautiful in every frame. Look for: </p><p>Brilliant-cut stones that reflect light evenly in photos<br/>Minimal, clean bands that make your hand look elegant<br/>Secure prong settings that lift the diamond enough for that iconic, light-catching tilt. </p><p>Some diamond shapes sparkle differently in different poses.<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-round\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Round cut \"> Round cut </a> and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-oval\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Oval cut\"> Oval cut</a> rings sparkle more in natural poses,<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-emerald\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Emerald cut\"> Emerald cut</a> rings look stunning in structured, editorial shots, pear and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-marquise\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Marquise cut \">Marquise cut </a>diamond rings demand hand poses that elongate the fingers, making the ring look even more dainty. Some metal colors photograph best on different skin tones. A yellow gold ring is perfect for someone with wheatish and deep skin tones, a rose gold complements cool tones, and white gold and platinum look universally regal. </p><p>Lucira Tip: To make the center stone look bigger, stack the ring with a thin eternity band or a single plain gold stack ring. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>A well crafted ring doesn’t need filters, harsh lighting or forced poses. It demands attention without seeking it in the most regular, mundane photos as well. If you want a ring that feels timeless on your hand but also photogenic in everyday moments, choosing a piece that balances craftsmanship with visual sparkle makes all the difference.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
